title: EEVblog 1509 - The Art of High Security Safe Locks (TEARDOWNS)

media:group.media:title: EEVblog 1509 - The Art of High Security Safe Locks (TEARDOWNS)
media:group.media:description:
A look at and teardown of three different types of Australian made high security Ross safe locks.
Ross 700 high security key lock
Ross 1000 Electronic keypad lock
Ross 1000 Bluetooth lock
https://rosslocks.com.au/

Part 2: More info, teardown of a TUVS Cablox 6 lever key design, and retrofitting an existing Guardall safe: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gsfDx7B9sks
BONUS video: Key safe lock comparison: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7xF1RCVw4Fc

00:00 - Mailbag
01:32 - Three different types of safe locks
05:54 - Which lock type is best?
06:59 - Visual and thermal attacks on Keypad locks
08:14 - Ross 700 High security 9 lever safe key lock Teardown!
11:35 - Ross 1000 series Keypad lock Teardown!
16:41 - Ross 1000 series Bluetooth Lock Teardown
17:32 - Magnetic attack?
18:08 - Gallium lock attack
